'''G<U+00E9>nies en herbe''' ('Budding Geniuses') was a [[T<U+00E9>l<U+00E9>vision de Radio-Canada|Radio-Canada]] [[television program]] in which students representing their ''[[Quebec education system|<U+00E9>cole secondaire]]'' ([[Quebec]] [[high school]]s) participated in [[trivia]] tournaments. ''[[Reach for the Top]]'' is an [[English Canada|English Canadian]] equivalent.

After the end of the TV series the tournaments continued under the aegis of several regional school organisations.

==Finals==
These are the finals of the G<U+00E9>nies en herbe tournaments, with the victors placed first.
